data.description: Stunning 1 story home in a great location. Home features both formals, split floor plan, gaslog FP, granite counters, dbl pane windows, hardi-plank siding, 4 ton Trane AC, tile & wood floors. Gorgeous backyard w/ large covered patio, & a fence lined with Jasmine. Copperfield amenities include parks, pools, tennis courts, greenbelts, jogging trails and 24-hour security patrol by the Harris County Sheriffs department. Home is also wired for an external generator. Just pick your size generator and you're ready to go. Make this you new home today! Won't last long at this price.
